de.polygonal.ds.HashableItem

type
class
implements
Hashable

An abstract object that provides an unique integer key.

Can be added to a HashSet or used as a key in a HashTable object.

Constructor

new()

Instance Variables

key : Int

A unique, unsigned 32-bit integer key.
A hash table transforms this key into an index of an array element by using a hash function.
This value should never be changed by the user.
